    {
      "key": "STORY_INTRO_ELARIA_FALL",
      "value": "Elaria was once a thriving land, where Science and Magic coexisted in harmony.\nThe order of the world was sustained by the Ancient Gate, which regulated the flow of primordial energy and preserved the fragile balance between Light and Darkness.\n\nThen came the Shattering.\nThe seals collapsed. The Gate was torn apart.\nLong-forgotten ancient beings — the Remnants — awakened and poured into the world, bringing chaos and annihilation.\n\nKingdoms fell one by one.\nMagic was cursed. The gods were denied.\nHumanity’s faith shattered no less than the world they once sought to protect.\n\nAnd from the ashes of that ruin…\na new story begins."
    },

